channel.title: What do you guys think?
channel.description:
Well, I was just arguing with a girl from my school, well not really arguing more as she was accusing me of being "gay", and she came out with this insult. Richo #38 05:32:54 pm yea would ya stfu already idc if i havent had a gf for ages why does it have to end like this//<3 matt 05:33:10 pm kyle ur a fucking weirdo all you seem to care about is ur motobike and ur a queer cunt
Hmm, and it just started to make me think that maybe she may have a point there. I mean, all I really care about is Motocross, and I've got to be the only 13 year old that couldn't care if I had a girlfriend or not.. But I'm not gay lol..
Well, what do you guys think, am I weird?

item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

Silver Lining:

You don’t know what weird really is. Weird is everyone, and everyone is weird. An illusion of the mind. If you ever join me, you’ll cast that foolish illusion off on the way.

True, although making others realize that is almost impossible. They’ll brand you as weird for saying they’re weird, because you act differently to everyone else in the environment you’re in (In my experience). It’s frustrating as fuck.

I haven’t liked any girls for a while, spending alot of time with my mates completely takes my mind off of them. It doesn’t mean I’m gay, but I am not saying that couldn’t be the reason.
